{
  "_comment": "ashlr-plugin MCP servers wired into OpenHands 1.6. Schema matches OpenHands' MCPConfig pydantic model (stdio_servers/sse_servers/shttp_servers arrays) — NOT the generic Claude Code mcpServers-dict format. Each stdio server runs a Bun-interpreted TypeScript MCP server. We mount the plugin read-only at /host/ashlr-plugin and a Linux-aarch64 bun binary at /host/bun (staged by scripts/start-openhands.sh since the host's bun is macOS-native). Plugin ships 10 MCP servers.",
